9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"K.G.F: Chapter 2 | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"The blood-soaked land of Kolar Gold Fields (KGF) has a new overlord now - Rocky, whose name strikes fear in the heart of his foes. His allies look up to Rocky as their Savior, the government sees him as a threat to law and order; enemies are clamoring for revenge and conspiring for his downfall. Bloodier battles and darker days await as Rocky continues on his quest for unchallenged supremacy."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/106192/k-g-f-chapter-2"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"K.G.F: Chapter 2"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"The blood-soaked land of Kolar Gold Fields (KGF) has a new overlord now - Rocky, whose name strikes fear in the heart of his foes. His allies look up to Rocky as their Savior, the government sees him as a threat to law and order; enemies are clamoring for revenge and conspiring for his downfall. Bloodier battles and darker days await as Rocky continues on his quest for unchallenged supremacy."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/106192/k-g-f-chapter-2"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/khNVygolU0TxLIDWff5tQlAhZ23.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"K.G.F: Chapter 2"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"The blood-soaked land of Kolar Gold Fields (KGF) has a new overlord now - Rocky, whose name strikes fear in the heart of his foes. His allies look up to Rocky 